urements presented in this\npaper can be used to test other galaxy formation models, and we make the\nmeasurements available online to facilitate this.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Sep 2015 20:06:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-09"}
