 superconductivity and spintronics to a\nnew research direction: super-spintronics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Sep 2015 01:36:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 30 Jan 2016 22:26:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-02"}
