te its deployability, we implement RCF as a Python\nmodule such that web developers can protect a critical server resource by\nadding only three lines of code.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Sep 2015 07:37:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-17"}
