 MPPCs would reduce the crosstalk to a much greater\nextent.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Sep 2015 08:43:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 Oct 2015 09:52:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-22"}
