 the effect of the intense required\nmagnetic fields is simulated along with specifically-written numerical codes in\nIDL.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Sep 2015 14:27:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-09"}
