donors, Mg and Fe, will\nhave a direct impact on the state of ionisation in ultra-cool atmospheres.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Sep 2015 08:47:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-04"}
